{"tid":535558,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN] 諾文尼亞 #1 連珠遊戲","createTime":"2018-01-21T04:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T08:12:10.000Z","uid":112375,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a3302e0dc6faa3085068d0b6982cec4dd1cf5a32","tid":535558,"uid":112375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/120754_cc35d4b8e796c869289176c383aa3da3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F120754_cc35d4b8e796c869289176c383aa3da3.png&h=b8989fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/120912_84ec719fb9d2423cda9690d77ae56706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F120912_84ec719fb9d2423cda9690d77ae56706.jpg&h=a8378d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/tw/app/id1296194248?l=zh&amp;ls=1&amp;mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Ftw%2Fapp%2Fid1296194248%3Fl%3Dzh%26ls%3D1%26mt%3D8&d=irIEEVvA7ca%2BemMB6FcfETM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=8393a265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/tw/app/id1296194248?l=zh&amp;ls=1&amp;mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\nAN: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.enjoygame.nwnytw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.enjoygame.nwnytw&d=irIEEVvA7ca%2BemMB6FcfETM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=37ad11f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.enjoygame.nwnytw</a><br />\n<br />\n遊戲簡介:<br />\n《諾文尼亞》將諸多經典元素融合在一起，開創了全新的連珠消除模式。可愛萌動的正統日漫畫風，一線CV熟悉的聲音，讓你在戰鬥的同時仿若親臨動漫；一線連珠的創新玩法讓你在休閒的同時，可以不斷挑戰策略極限；分分鐘就可以上手，隨時隨地暢享連珠快感！ <br />\n<br />\n【遊戲特色】<br />\n**連珠消除 全新玩法高能出擊**<br />\n開創性的連珠消除玩法，多種特效炫目暴擊，前所未有的劇情式策略消除遊戲體驗。<br />\n<br />\n**卡牌收集 召喚養成盡在掌控**<br />\n數百個英雄等待你去收集，强化、覺醒、升級，培養你專屬的完美戰隊。<br />\n<br />\n**華麗戰鬥 3D場景真實呈現**<br />\n打破壁壘，2D混搭3D，多重方式展示完美畫面品質；戰鬥場景全3D立體呈現，多視角切換，實體化戰鬥無縫鏈接，極緻戰鬥體驗如臨其境。<br />\n<br />\n**新式RPG 百變作戰隨時暢享**<br />\n連珠引發二次元英雄大作戰，屬性剋制、英雄搭配、專屬技能，各種策略隨你操縱。<br />\n<br />\n**炫酷技能 體驗火爆激戰快感**<br />\n炫目華麗的技能效果，一擊必殺的炫酷快感，為你帶來酣暢淋漓的戰鬥體驗。<br />\n<br />\n**守護精靈 職業突破無限爆發**<br />\n最新式的職業守護精靈系統，突破性潛力提升，讓你的團隊戰力大爆發，沒有最强，只有更强。<br />\n<br />\n**知名聲優 豪華陣容傾力助陣**<br />\n日本頂尖級別聲優傾情獻聲，爲你帶來絕對豪華的聽覺盛宴，激戰快感再攀巔峰。<br />\n<br />\n**燒腦策略 打造終極强力戰隊**<br />\n不同戰隊搭配，不同戰鬥體驗，每個英雄都有其專屬技能，最佳戰隊如何成就，盡在你掌控之中。<br />\n<br />\n**完美團隊 冒險之旅携手而戰**<br />\n强大的組隊玩法，和你的好友共同橫掃一切艱難險阻，神秘副本，冒險之旅，各種挑戰並肩而戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　"},{"pid":"8c90aeb6544be9ebcd9fa2492cc783b7c8321c6b","tid":535558,"uid":112375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"見無人講開個POST比玩既人可以討論下"},{"pid":"e088151f5214ba370d072c0b57aa882def272078","tid":535558,"uid":30952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:45:24.000Z","msg":"支那驚"},{"pid":"a86beae249397ceafb6e25a8ba8be7ba7dc19025","tid":535558,"uid":112375,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T05:51:20.000Z","msg":"no la japan game"},{"pid":"204af20c4d13d9d763593759989c17d6176de09a","tid":535558,"uid":60099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T13:40:48.000Z","msg":"見到VIP 都怕怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7815acba4c467c1bf2b1ab54d5306fab8fe458ba","tid":535558,"uid":37853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"玩法係好<br />\n但 VIP 制<br />\n10抽要打到2x lv<br />\n見到都唔想開坑"},{"pid":"6bf35a09d785e6442b1b2b80d8cbd563ef381418","tid":535558,"uid":49808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:49:57.000Z","msg":"2ser...<br />\n玩到灌木王關卡左 應該點打<br />\n1RD就得返3分1血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm